  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118790/extras/4737ccf435b818b62c54c1ab70006724.avif?t=1718456290\" width=616 height=184 /></span><br>Enter an amazing and challenging world!<br>VQD is a casual game that promises to make you adventure through four diverse environments consisting of platforms, secret places and various enemies to defeat!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118790/extras/09e0fc92b030d042dcc9df7836bdd2ea.poster.avif?t=1718456290\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118790/extras/09e0fc92b030d042dcc9df7836bdd2ea.webm?t=1718456290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118790/extras/09e0fc92b030d042dcc9df7836bdd2ea.mp4?t=1718456290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>24 levels to clear;<br></li><li>22 achievements to achieve;<br></li><li>Variety of enemies;<br></li><li>Secret environments;<br></li><li>Various outfits and weapons to make you stronger.</li></ul><br><strong>Face these challenges like never before!</strong>",
